1.0 About
Ropeclient is a text based virtual tabletop for roleplaying online.

- Project homepage: http://www.eiden.fi/ropeclient
- Discussion: http://groups.google.com/group/ropeclient


2.0 Development notes
Currently no public server is running. Development focuses on dev branch 
and updates are pulled to master when appropriate.

3.0 Ropeclient Server Installation notes
- Requires python 3
- Python Autobahn http://autobahn.ws/python/
- Redis for backend database http://redis.io/

3.0 Usage
- Run server with python3 server.py
- Open with browser the webclient index page

4.0 Development Roadmap
Upgrading slowly features from the Python 2 version to the latest 
version.
